---
import BentoItem from './BentoItem.astro'
---
<section
    class={`
        w-full max-w-[1400px] 
        grid grid-cols-10 auto-rows-[30rem] gap-4
        mx-auto p-20
    `}>

   <BentoItem 
        class="col-sapn-10 md:col-span-4" 
        title="ANDORRA: EL CÉNIT DE LOS PREMIOS ESLAND"
    >

    <div 
        slot="image"
        class="absolute left-0 top-00 bottom-0 h-full group-hover:scale-110 transition-scale duration-1000 ease-in-out opacity-90 bg-blend-luminosity bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-blue-950 -z-10"
        style="background-image: url('/mountain.webp')"
    >
    </div>
        <p slot="content" class="max-w-xl">
            Este año, el momento de la alfombra azul será sustituido y mejorado, gracias a los increíbles paisajes andorranos, por una <strong>alfombra blanca en plena nieve</strong> , situada en las <strong>pistas de esquí de Andorra.</strong> 
        </p>

   </BentoItem>

   <BentoItem class="col-sapn-10 md:col-span-6" title="LA ALFOMBRA BLANCA" subtitle="16 de febrero de 2024">
    <div 
    slot="image"
    class="absolute left-0 top-00 bottom-0 h-full group-hover:scale-110 transition-scale duration-1000 ease-in-out opacity-90 bg-blend-luminosity bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-blue-950 -z-10"
    style="background-image: url('/mountain.webp')"
>
</div>

   </BentoItem>

   <BentoItem class="col-sapn-10 md:col-span-6" title="LA GALA" subtitle="17 de febrero de 2024">
    <div 
    slot="image"
    class="absolute left-0 top-00 bottom-0 h-full group-hover:scale-110 transition-scale duration-1000 ease-in-out opacity-90 bg-blend-luminosity bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-blue-950 -z-10"
    style="background-image: url('/mountain.webp')"
>
</div>
    </BentoItem>

   <BentoItem class="col-sapn-10 md:col-span-4" title="DISFRUTA DEL REDDIT DE LA COMUNIDAD">
    <div 
    slot="image"
    class="absolute left-0 top-00 bottom-0 h-full group-hover:scale-110 transition-scale duration-1000 ease-in-out opacity-90 bg-blend-luminosity bg-center bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-blue-950 -z-10"
    style="background-image: url('/mountain.webp')"
>
</div>
   </BentoItem>

</section>